"{\"uid\": \"flotrack.org-articles-12762426-aau-junior-olympics-2024-champions-list\", \"text\": \"Adidas Indoor Nationals  Texas Distance Festival  Chandler Rotary Invite  W&L Outdoor T&F Carnival  Run Rome the Marathon  David Noble Relays  Emory Thrills in the Hills  WashU Distance Carnival  Jim Taylor Duals  Doc Jopson Invitational  2026 FSU Relays  Continental Tour: Maurie Plant Meet  WashU Invite  Monmouth Home Opener  Corsair Classic  As theAAU Junior Olympics track and field meet 2024concludes on Day 8, the excitement and action has been non-stop \\u00a0throughout the event.  Over the course of the competition, numerous champions emerged, showcasing remarkable talent and dedication.  One of the most famous events, the 200m dash, had standout performances delivered by Saleia Stoew and Cerenity Bell among the youngest competitors, while Keyzelle Thomas and Liam Jones shone in the older age groups.  Here is the complete list of AAU Junior Olympics 2024 winners.  \\u2022 Theresa Albertson - Southern Jersey Track and Field - 7:26.60  \\u2022 Logan Alsobrook - Elite Feet Performance - 2:15.93  The 2024 Junior Olympics Track and Field competition isstreaming live on FloTrack, MileSplit and the FloSports app.Highlights, replays and breaking news are on both platforms.  Do not miss all the track and field season action streaming on FloTrack.Check out the FloTrack schedule for more events.  Video footage from each event will be archived and stored in a video library for FloTrack subscribers to watch for the duration of their subscriptions.    Tags:  Get the most important Track & Field stories delivered straight to your inbox.  \\u00a92006 - Present FloSports, Inc. All rights reserved.\"}"